author: COMSOL
description: This example demonstrates the Lithium-Ion Battery, Single-Ion Conductor interface for studying the discharge of a lithium-ion battery with solid electrolyte. The behavior at various discharge currents and solid electrolyte conductivities is analyzed. The geometry is in one dimension and the model is isothermal.
label: li_battery_solid_electrolyte.mph
